layouts.name: slanted_map
layouts.label: Slanted Map Background with Image and Copy

sub_fields.label: Background Left/Right Position
sub_fields.name: slanted_map_bg_position
sub_fields.instructions: Aligns the map background to the left or right. The foreground image will automatically fix to the direction of the map background.

sub_fields.label: Image Middle/Bottom Alignment
sub_fields.name: slanted_map_image_vertical_alignment
sub_fields.instructions:
Aligning "Middle" will make the foreground image fix to the vertical middle of its container.
Aligning "Bottom" will make the foreground image fix to the bottom of its container.

sub_fields.label: Image Center/Left/Right Alignment
sub_fields.name: slanted_map_image_horizontal_alignment
sub_fields.instructions:
Aligning "Center" will make the foreground image float in the center of its container.
Aligning "Left" will make the foreground image float to the left of its container.
Aligning "Right" will make the foreground image float to the right of its container.

sub_fields.label: Copy Block Text
sub_fields.name: slanted_map_copy_block_text
sub_fields.instructions: Use only "Heading 6" for adding a title to a block of text.
